name: FNF - Vs. Weegee Full Week
description:
The nostalgic nightmare that haunted the internet in the 2000's is back with a vengeance! Take on Weegee, known from YTPs like "The Sky Had a Weegee", in a new original song by yours truly! 

The mod features: 
-New sprite sheet for Weegee
-New original 2 minute song, also called "Weegee"
-One hella fast chart
-A new green static background
-Dialogue for Weegee
-UI changes
-comedic reference
